                "Dialogue"
            ],
            [
                "Another day slowly dragging out at school."
            ],
            [
                "The students are yawning every couple of seconds."
            ],
            [
                "It feels even more tiring to have to write all the mumbo jumbo on the sheets."
            ],
            [
                "I accidentally bump out a pen from my desk."
            ],
            [
                "Hey, this is yours I think."
            ],
            [
                "Oh, hey. I know you."
            ],
            [
                "I know you too."
            ],
            [
                "Yeah, What's my name then?"
            ],
            [
                "Easy. [tn]. Your turn, what was I wearing that day?"
            ],
            [
                "uuuuhhh ..........."
            ],
            [
                "You frankly can't recall if that happened two days ago or a month ago."
            ],
            [
                "Ugh, sorry, I'm barely keeping up with the class, how do you manage to not fall asleep."
            ],
            [
                "Sheer magic I'd say."
            ],
            [
                "You are not complete sure if [he] meant the actual magic, or some form of game called Magic."
            ],
            [
                "A message pops up. Its Victor."
            ],
            [
                "Hey, it's me Victor. From the coffee shop. :)"
            ],
            [
                "Are you free? Really been trashy today, got something I wanna show you."
